00:06:09.865 --> 00:06:12.426
Uh-oh, he's coming.
Minamikawa closes the distance.

00:06:12.646 --> 00:06:17.246
Circling that way is scary. If his feet
stop, Shinichi's getting caught.

00:06:18.246 --> 00:06:20.646
