Shinichi uses his footwork.

00:06:28.446 --> 00:06:30.306
Footwork, footwork.
Go, go, go.

00:06:30.306 --> 00:06:31.786
How's this, how's this?
Oh!

00:06:31.786 --> 00:06:35.146
