Now Shinichi fires back.

00:06:35.267 --> 00:06:37.567
What even is this?
What kind of match is this?

00:06:38.367 --> 00:06:40.467
Shitara-san, this is lasting longer than
expected.

00:06:41.067 --> 00:06:45.607
When you think about it, this is basically
no different from a knife. Exactly.

00:06:46.267 --> 00:06:50.187
It really is.
It's basically a knife.

00:06:50.647 --> 00:06:54.547
This is the kind of thing you want to
watch while eating steak. That's some rich-guy shit.

00:06:54.547 --> 00:06:59.248
It's already gone way long. Shinichi's
footwork is holding up, just like that claim he can still run in the sixes.

00:06:59.928 --> 00:07:01.388
Ah, he's switching hands.
Yeah.

00:07:02.388 --> 00:07:04.708
