Go, go, go, go!

00:07:04.708 --> 00:07:10.228
Shinichi keeps switching. And now
Minamikawa puts that lead hand out again.

00:07:10.228 --> 00:07:12.728
He's going after that hand.
Right.

00:07:12.728 --> 00:07:14.228
So close.
Yeah, he's mixing high and low.

00:07:14.868 --> 00:07:18.608
In terms of footwork, this is completely
Shinichi's edge. Yeah, he's disrupting him.

00:07:18.728 --> 00:07:21.288
Right.
He's varying high and low.

00:07:23.509 --> 00:07:27.129
Whoa, whoa - has Shinichi finally been
cornered? Whoa, whoa.

00:07:27.449 --> 00:07:29.149
That was close.
Oh!

00:07:29.669 --> 00:07:30.949
Oh!
To the body, to the body.

00:07:31.109 --> 00:07:32.709
Didn't land.
Didn't land.

00:07:33.109 --> 00:07:37.649
