They're both getting tired now.

00:07:48.150 --> 00:07:50.050
Minamikawa's breathing hard.
Oh, now Shinichi...

00:07:50.050 --> 00:07:50.790
Whoa.
Whoa.

00:07:50.790 --> 00:07:53.830
He got him.
He got him.

00:07:55.010 --> 00:07:56.310
That's Shinichi.
Whoa.

00:07:56.330 --> 00:07:58.770
Whoa.

00:08:02.666 --> 00:08:04.326
Right there.
No, no, he got him.

00:08:04.686 --> 00:08:07.966
